Type: Package
Package: ggNetView.shiny
Title: Interactive Shiny Interface for 'ggNetView'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yue", "Liu", , "yueliu@iae.ac.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6180-8068")),
    person("Chao", "Wang", , "cwang@iae.ac.cn", role = "aut"))
Description: A 'shinydashboard' based graphical user interface for the
    'ggNetView' R package. Provides interactive workflows for building
    correlation / co-occurrence networks, visualizing them with
    publication-quality 'ggraph' / 'ggplot2' layouts, computing network
    topology metrics including zi-pi node-role analysis, and exploring
    multi-block environment-species associations via 'gglink_heatmaps'.
    Supports both the built-in example datasets shipped with 'ggNetView'
    and user-uploaded files (CSV / TSV / RDS).
